@startuml
actor Client
participant "ManagerController\n(DTO Layer)" as ManagerController
participant "ManagerService\n(Business Logic)" as ManagerService
participant "ManagerRepository\n(Entity Layer)" as ManagerRepository
database DB

Client -> ManagerController : POST /managers\nmanagerDTO
note right of ManagerController: Validación automática del DTO\n(@Valid, @NotNull, etc.)

ManagerController -> ManagerService : createManager(managerDTO)
note right of ManagerService: Aplica lógica de negocio:\n- Mapea DTO -> Entity\n- Verifica club existente\n- Reglas de negocio (ej.: un club solo puede tener 1 manager)

ManagerService -> ManagerRepository : save(manager)
ManagerRepository -> DB : INSERT INTO manager ...
DB --> ManagerRepository : OK / generated id
ManagerRepository --> ManagerService : Manager entity

ManagerService --> ManagerController : ManagerDTO
ManagerController --> Client : 201 Created\nmanagerDTO
@enduml
